This addon will re-format the .imdb file. Currently, there are five different
formats you can use - more will be added in time (maybe).

Here follows a quick output of how the different formats look like:

format 1:

.---------------------------------|iMDB|-----------------------------------.
|                                                                          |
|                         Kill Bill: Vol. 1 (2003)                         |
|                                                                          |
|                    http://us.imdb.com/title/tt0266697                    |
