| genre...: Action, Crime, Thriller        | A female assassin attacked on |
| score...: [********--]  8.2 20,692 votes | her wedding day by her group  |
| director: Quentin Tarantino              | leader, Bill, wakes up from a |
| rated...: USA:R      runtime.: 111 min   | coma and seeks revenge.       |
| country.: USA        language: Englis... |                               |
| starring: Uma Thurman                    |                               |
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Number of screens: 3,102                                                 |
| Premiered in.....: Singapore 17 October 2003                             |
`------------------------------------------------------------| 2003 psxc |-'


