Title........: Kill Bill: Vol. 1 (2003) 
-
IMDb Link....: http://us.imdb.com/title/tt0266697
Directed by..: Quentin Tarantino
Genre........: Action / Crime / Thriller
User Rating..: 8.2/10 (20,692 votes) top 250: #100
Tagline......: In the year 2003, Uma Thurman will kill Bill
-
Country......: USA
Language.....: English / Japanese / French
Certification: Australia:R / Canada:18A / Canada:R / Finland:K-18 / 
Premiere Date: Singapore 17 October 2003
Runtime......: 111 min
-
